page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Service with the JavaScript SDK to generate images'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first image generation call with the JavaScript SDK.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free- LTS versions of Node.js- An Azure OpenAI resource created in the East US region. For more information, see Create a resource and deploy a model with Azure OpenAI.
